{"type":"message","id":"fb11843e","parentId":"2cffa524","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:23:49.780Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_w623c4j9nkq2_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5068\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3156\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\n[mutation proposed] the\n[master c48e705] pulse: 2026-03-24 112315\n 6 files changed, 330 insertions(+), 78 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 112315.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 112315.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 112215.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 112315 - CFI analysis revealed that 94.3% of frequency-invariants have CFI<0.7, meaning frequency-based compression mostly captures metaprogramming artifacts (process noise) rather than actual research trajectory. The experiment design exists but needs implementation."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"clear-ember","total":10,"totalLines":10,"totalChars":750,"truncated":false,"exitCode":0,"name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774365829778}}
